reviewDescription: I read all the reviews on this iPhone listing/seller and I knew that I might receive a scratched up iPhone or a stolen iPhone or a bad battery. Not one single scratch, not stolen (I looked up the IMEI and found a website to check), battery is 100% and it recognizes my SIM card, same value from buying one straight from Apple Store (if I’m not mistaken with the IMEI screenshot I attached, I think I still have a good half a year warranty with Apple Store!)

reviewDescription: recently purchased a refurbished iPhone 13, and I must say that I am incredibly impressed with the quality of this device. As someone who values performance, functionality, and style, I was initially skeptical about buying a refurbished phone, but the experience has been nothing short of amazing. Here is my detailed review of the refurbished iPhone 13.Design and Build Quality:The iPhone 13 has a sleek and stylish design that makes it stand out from other smartphones in the market. The build quality is excellent, and the phone feels solid in your hand. The phone's aluminum frame and ceramic shield front cover make it incredibly durable, ensuring that it can withstand accidental drops and scratches.Performance:The refurbished iPhone 13 performs just as well as a brand new device, thanks to its powerful A15 Bionic chip. The phone is incredibly responsive, and apps load quickly, making it ideal for multitasking and running demanding applications. The camera quality is excellent, and the device's image processing capabilities are impressive, resulting in stunning images and videos.Battery Life:The battery life of the iPhone 13 is excellent, and the refurbished device holds up just as well as a brand new device. The phone's battery can last an entire day, even with heavy usage, making it ideal for those who are always on the go.Value for Money:The refurbished iPhone 13 offers excellent value for money. The device is significantly cheaper than a brand new device, yet it performs just as well. The phone is also backed by a warranty, giving you peace of mind that your investment is protected.Environmental Impact:Buying a refurbished iPhone 13 is an eco-friendly choice that reduces e-waste and helps conserve the environment. By choosing to purchase a refurbished device, you are contributing to the reduction of the carbon footprint caused by the production of new devices.Overall, I am incredibly impressed with the refurbished iPhone 13. The device's design, performance, and battery life are excellent, and the value for money is unmatched. The phone is an excellent investment for anyone who wants a high-quality smartphone without breaking the bank. The eco-friendly aspect of purchasing a refurbished device is also a significant bonus. I highly recommend the refurbished iPhone 13 to anyone looking for a high-quality smartphone at an affordable price.

reviewDescription: Pedi este articulo "reacondicionado" el precio sigue siendo bastante alto si somos honestos, no es un articulo economico para aceptar recibir articulos de tan mala presentacion, el que me llego no solo no era el color que seleccione, si no que ademas la bocina sonaba mal, como si estuviera dañada. Llegue a pensar que podia pasarlo por alto, ya que necesitaba un telefono urgentemente, sin embargo la gota que derramo el vaso fue notal que en el lateral tenia lo que parecia dos bastantemente visible hoyos, que se veian relleados y pintados.La bateria al 90% lo cual esta en la descripcion y esta bien, sin embargo prometen un articulo "como nuevo" con detalles poco visibles, lo cual no es lo que recibes, me impresiono que me mandaran un telefono con tan visibles y grandes defectos, y lo cobran bastante bien. Lo regrese y recibi mi reembolso sin problemas, sin embargo esto me dejo un buen rato sin mobil, no lo recomiendo, mas vale invertir eso que te ahorras en uno nuevo para evitar estos contratiempos.
reviewTitle: No vuelvo a ordernar un articulo reacondicionado.
